name: condomAnime
description:
Trained on grapefruit model but seems to work fine with most hentai models.

Simple Lora to make realistic sized penises with condoms. You don't need to use keywords but it does help.

Captions were trained with (unused condom) and (used condom) but doesn't work very well.

Captions were trained with colors. Tagging a color seems to help, e.g. white condom, green condom, pink condom etc.

This is my first model of anykind so be gentle. It's not perfect and takes some seed gacha due to the difficulty in finding quality condom pictures.
